*** Paragraph 5
	Enforcing laws fiercely does not guarantee justice. High class criminal
	cases where large organizations like banks or stock investment firms are
	curropt may receive disproportionate punishments. Many occassions where
	investment firms steal hundreds of millions of dollars from the working
	class only to be faced with fines that relatively amount to pennies on the
